metadata.name: VENDETTA OG #1
metadata.description: This NFT entitles the holder to various benefits as an OG. This includes a higher APR boost in conjunction with VEN holdings, Fee-Free staking, and early access to all feature sets introduced within the Protocol. This also grants access to the Vendetta Finance governance discord channel where holders can participate in decision making and protocol health matters with the Multi-Sig Treasurers and Senior Advisors.
